graph UTTER2
END6288
      ?= OBTAIN6267
           ?= OBTAIN-BY-ASKING6213
                S1 -> REQUEST6164
                     ?= INDIRECT-REQUEST6114
                          S -> SURFACE-QUESTION6095
  (SURFACE-QUESTION6095 INDIRECT-REQUEST6114 REQUEST6164 OBTAIN-BY-ASKING6213 OBTAIN6267 EN
D6288)
